            class="mb-4"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-medium mb-4">Inconsistent Processes</h3>
        <p class="font-light">
          Manual steps leading to human errors, inconsistent customer
          experiences, or vital tasks falling through the cracks?
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-sm">
        <div class="flex justify-center opacity-80">
          <img
            width="56"
            height="56"
            src="https://img.icons8.com/glyph-neue/64/road-worker.png"
            alt="road-worker"
            style="filter: invert(96%) sepia(1%) saturate(5788%) hue-rotate(182deg) brightness(85%) contrast(101%);"
            class="mb-4"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-normal mb-4">Disconnected Systems</h3>
        <p class="font-light">
          Struggling with data silos because your essential SaaS tools and
          platforms don't talk to each other effectively?
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="p-6 border rounded-sm">
        <div class="flex justify-center opacity-80">
          <img
            width="56"
            height="56"
            src="https://img.icons8.com/glyph-neue/64/artificial-intelligence.png"
            alt="artificial-intelligence"
            style="filter: invert(96%) sepia(1%) saturate(5788%) hue-rotate(182deg) brightness(85%) contrast(101%);"
            class="mb-4"
          />
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-normal mb-4">Focus Diverted</h3>
        <p class="font-light">
          Is your team bogged down by tedious, repetitive work instead of
          focusing on strategic initiatives and core product development?
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

